## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **sepsis 30-day mortality** = ~20-30%, septic shock ~40%. quantum-VQE 의 임상 efficacy 보장 X.
2. **TLR4 antagonist failures** — eritoran (TAK-242) phase III fail in 2013. sepsis 의 mechanism complexity 보여줌. quantum-VQE 의 selectivity 향상 path.
3. **drotrecogin alfa Xigris withdrawal 2011** = activated protein C in sepsis failed in PROWESS-SHOCK RCT. evidence-based clinical trials 의 importance.
4. **vasopressors empirical** — norepinephrine first-line, mechanism-specific design 가능.
5. **mechanical ventilation 약 부재** — ventilator-induced lung injury (VILI) prevention 약물 부재. PEEP / Vt strategy 가 standard.
6. **ICU delirium** = 30-80% incidence, 단 약물 효과 limited. dexmedetomidine 만 partial evidence.
7. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, ICU 임상 의미 한정. emergency setting 의 quantum-design drug 응용 어려움.

